3.5 Create BC & OR Invocation report  
a. Login by Maker   
Step 1: Click invocation button. Total disruption or partial disruption can be selected under “disruption type”. Select the start date and start 
time of disruption as well as end date and end time. Maker needs to record disruptions occurred during the activity under all heads along 
with impact tolerance category as per categories given under services & BIA head. Impact Tolerance needs to be filled in accordance with 
the table at the bottom right. All the fields need to be mandatorily filled in order to move to the next stage. Click “Save and Next” to visit 
next page.  
21  
Step 2: Resilience level needs to be selected based on depth of the disruption and its impact on operations. Validate and then click on 
submit to send to Checker for review.  
22 
